White has control over the light squares.}) 13. Ne3 {can be well met by} (13.
c3 g5 14. Bg3 ({The aggressive} 14. Nxg5 $6 hxg5 15. Bxg5 Kg7 16. Qf3 Rb8 17.
Rab1 Kg6 18. h4 bxc3 19. bxc3 Bg4 20. Qg3 Qd7 21. Ne3 Bxe3 22. Qxe3 Nh7 {
