exd4 15. cxd4 cxd4 16. Nxd4 Nxd4 17. Qxd4 Be6 18. Ne3 (18. Ng3 {transposes to
13.Ng3}) 18... Rc8 19. a4 {This was Smirin, I - Beliavsky, A Netanya 2009
